    "translation":{"eng":"Worship Śrī Gaura-Gadādhara, Śrī Advaita, and the original guru Śrī Nityānanda Prabhu (knowing Gaura and Kṛṣṇa to be the same, and knowing guru to be very dear to Kṛṣṇa). Also remember Mahāprabhu’s intimate associates, Śrīvāsa Paṇḍita, Haridāsa Ṭhākura, Murāri Gupta, and Mukunda Datta. (Absorbed in love of Gaura, remember them, just remember them!)"}},{
